<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='942000' id='t-942000'>And if somebody answers, that shall be my wish.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:56
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='945000' id='t-945000'>So she went up to each and said, &quot;Do you accept that I have defeated you?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='949000' id='t-949000'>And they said, &quot;Me? Defeated by a woman?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='951000' id='t-951000'>No way, that's impossible! No no no no no! That's not possible.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='955000' id='t-955000'>Till finally one prince said,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='957000' id='t-957000'>&quot;Princess, I accept, you have defeated me.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='963000' id='t-963000'>&quot;Uh-huh ...&quot; she said.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='965000' id='t-965000'>&quot;Father, mother, this man shall be my wife.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='969000' id='t-969000'>(Whistling)</span>
</span>
</p>
